## Ethical & Legal Notice
This repository is protected under the Digital Crystal Protocol.  
- Any use of SDKP, SD&N, QCC0, LLAL, or DCP components **must cite Donald Paul Smith and the canonical CID**.  
- Commercial or derivative use requires enforcement of the **7% royalty** to `FatherTimeSDKP.eth`.  
- AI-generated outputs must maintain a **verifiable audit trail** using the SolidifyEvent logging system.

